content:
A bunch of statements can be placed in braces to be executed as a single block. Such a block of statements can be named or be provided with a condition for execution. Below is how you'd place a series of statements in a block.Code section 3.7: A statement block.


1 {
2     int a = 10;
3     int b = 20;
4     int result = a + b;
5 }
